data.overview: Seven noble families fight for control of the mythical land of Westeros. Friction between the houses leads to full-scale war. All while a very ancient evil awakens in the farthest north. Amidst the war, a neglected military order of misfits, the Night's Watch, is all that stands between the realms of men and the icy horrors beyond.
A spoof/parody Based on HBO's hit series "A Game of Thrones" and George RR Martin's A Song of Ice and Fire

aliases: Hip Hop Tribe 2: Game of Thrones
data.overview: Tribe of Hip Hop (Hangul: 힙합의 민족) is a hip hop competition program where celebrities with little-to-no background in hip hop are teamed up with professional hip hop music producers.
